>> Ah, it's raining like this?

510
00:36:37,396 --> 00:36:40,332
(Minseok) It wasn't raining yet when I came out.

511
00:36:40,399 --> 00:36:42,834
>> When did you leave?

512
00:36:42,901 --> 00:36:44,836
(Minseok) About two hours ago.

513
00:36:44,903 --> 00:36:47,839
>> So long ago?

514
00:36:47,906 --> 00:36:49,841
No, no way...

515
00:36:49,908 --> 00:36:51,343
(Minseok) Huh?

516
00:36:51,410 --> 00:36:56,915
>> On the way home, I heard that there was an accident in the neighborhood.

517
00:36:59,418 --> 00:37:01,420
Minseok!

518
00:37:03,622 --> 00:37:31,516
♪～

519
00:37:31,583 --> 00:37:33,518
(Momoko) [It's okay]

520
00:37:33,585 --> 00:37:45,530
♪～

521
00:37:45,597 --> 00:37:47,032
(Momoko) Wow!

522
00:37:47,099 --> 00:37:48,533
Ah.

523
00:37:48,600 --> 00:37:57,542
♪～

524
00:37:57,609 --> 00:38:01,546
📱(Ring tone)

525
00:38:01,613 --> 00:38:03,548
📱(Voice guidance) I called you, but...

526
00:38:03,615 --> 00:38:05,117
📱(Call ending sound)

527
00:38:06,618 --> 00:38:11,556
(Momoko) Huh… hah…｡

528
00:38:14,059 --> 00:38:16,495
(Minseok) Momoko Sensei.

529
00:38:16,561 --> 00:38:18,563
Mr. Peach!

530
00:38:20,565 --> 00:38:24,069
(Momoko) Hahaha...｡

531
00:38:28,073 --> 00:38:32,010
(Momoko) Hahaha...｡

532
00:38:32,077 --> 00:38:34,579
[It's okay! ]

533
00:38:37,082 --> 00:38:39,084
(Father) [Peach! 〕

534
00:38:47,092 --> 00:38:49,594
(Momoko) Huh…｡

535
00:38:51,096 --> 00:38:53,098
(Minseok) Momoko-sensei!

536
00:38:56,101 --> 00:38:59,104
(Minseok) Momoko-sensei, are you okay?

537
00:39:01,106 --> 00:39:03,041
OK?

538
00:39:03,108 --> 00:39:05,110
(Momoko) Minseok-san.

539
00:39:09,114 --> 00:39:13,485
(Momoko) I'm sorry, I'm sorry...

540
00:39:13,552 --> 00:39:17,989
(cry)

541
00:39:18,056 --> 00:39:20,492
sorry….

542
00:39:20,559 --> 00:39:23,495
(cry)

543
00:39:23,562 --> 00:39:26,498
I'm sorry... (Sound of a car approaching)

544
00:39:26,565 --> 00:39:28,500
(Sound of car door closing) (Takuto) Momoko!

545
00:39:28,567 --> 00:39:32,571
(Momoko) I'm sorry, I'm sorry...

546
00:39:51,089 --> 00:39:53,091
(Minseok) Does it hurt?

547
00:39:59,097 --> 00:40:01,099
(Momoko) It's okay.

548
00:40:12,043 --> 00:40:14,045
(Peach) Private…｡

549
00:40:17,549 --> 00:40:20,051
(Peach) 23 years ago…｡

550
00:40:26,057 --> 00:40:29,060
(Momoko) The day I lost my father...

551
00:40:31,563 --> 00:40:34,499
>> [Look, Momoko, it's cold today. You're going to catch a cold. Please wear some clothes.]

552
00:40:34,566 --> 00:40:37,502
(Momoko) [Okay] >> [Go wear it]

553
00:40:37,569 --> 00:40:41,006
(Momoko) [It's okay! ]

554
00:40:41,072 --> 00:40:44,509
(Father) [Peach Peach]

555
00:40:44,576 --> 00:40:47,512
(Momoko's voice) It's cold so you'll catch a cold →

556
00:40:47,579 --> 00:40:51,583
The gentle hands of a concerned father...

557
00:40:54,586 --> 00:40:56,588
(Momoko) I shook it off.

558
00:41:03,094 --> 00:41:08,099
(Momoko) Just like that, we never met again.

559
00:41:14,539 --> 00:41:19,477
(Momoko) Dad...

560
00:41:19,544 --> 00:41:24,549
Gone forever before me.

561
00:41:31,556 --> 00:41:35,994
(Momoko) Minseok-san today too→

562
00:41:36,061 --> 00:41:38,496
Thank you for worrying →

563
00:41:38,563 --> 00:41:44,069
I'm irritated...

564
00:41:47,072 --> 00:41:53,078
(Momoko) She shook off Minseok-san's gentle hand.

565
00:41:59,084 --> 00:42:02,520
(Momoko) Parting with someone→

566
00:42:02,587 --> 00:42:07,525
Even though I don't know when I'll visit →

567
00:42:07,592 --> 00:42:10,595
I do that...

568
00:42:14,599 --> 00:42:17,535
(Momoko) I should know this so much it hurts.

569
00:42:17,602 --> 00:42:34,052
♪～

570
00:42:34,119 --> 00:42:38,556
(Minseok) I...

571
00:42:38,623 --> 00:42:40,625
I'm here.

572
00:42:44,629 --> 00:42:48,066
(Minseok) Momoko Sensei →

573
00:42:48,133 --> 00:42:51,569
If you need it→

574
00:42:51,636 --> 00:42:56,641
I've been here forever.

575
00:43:05,650 --> 00:43:07,585
(Momoko) Thank you.

576
00:43:07,652 --> 00:43:17,028
♪～

577
00:43:17,095 --> 00:43:19,030
>> Oh, sorry.

578
00:43:19,097 --> 00:43:21,533
Momoko... Where is Momoko Kawase's hospital room?

579
00:43:21,599 --> 00:43:23,535
(Reception) Momoko Kawase.

580
00:43:23,601 --> 00:43:37,048
♪～

581
00:43:37,115 --> 00:43:40,051
(sound of door opening)

582
00:43:40,118 --> 00:43:57,569
♪～

583
00:43:57,635 --> 00:43:59,571
(Takuto) Momoko is okay now.

584
00:43:59,637 --> 00:44:02,574
Minor bruises and concussion.

585
00:44:02,640 --> 00:44:05,143
I can go home tomorrow.

586
00:44:08,146 --> 00:44:12,517
(Takuto) Hey, Minchok, are you okay?

587
00:44:12,584 --> 00:44:15,520
Aren't you hurt?

588
00:44:15,587 --> 00:44:17,589
(Minseok) It's okay.

589
00:44:19,090 --> 00:44:21,526
(Takuto) I see.

590
00:44:21,593 --> 00:44:25,597
Then go home and rest today.

591
00:44:28,099 --> 00:44:30,535
(Minseok) No.

592
00:44:30,602 --> 00:44:32,037
(Takuto) Huh?

593
00:44:32,103 --> 00:44:35,040
(Minseok) I'm here.

594
00:44:35,106 --> 00:44:37,042
(Takuto) What are you saying?

595
00:44:37,108 --> 00:44:39,544
(Minseok) I'll always be here.

596
00:44:39,611 --> 00:44:41,546
(Takuto) What's wrong, Minchok?

597
00:44:41,613 --> 00:44:46,551
(Minseok) While searching for Momoko-sensei →

598
00:44:46,618 --> 00:44:50,055
I've always regretted it.

599
00:44:50,121 --> 00:44:52,557
(Takuto) Regret?

600
00:44:52,624 --> 00:44:56,561
(Minseok) Why faster→

601
00:44:56,628 --> 00:44:59,130
I guess you didn't notice.

602
00:45:02,634 --> 00:45:05,570
(Minseok) Momoko-sensei is for me →

603
00:45:05,637 --> 00:45:08,139
very….

604
00:45:10,575 --> 00:45:14,579
He's a very, very important person.

605
00:45:24,589 --> 00:45:33,531
♪～

606
00:45:33,598 --> 00:45:37,035
(Takuto) More than you →

607
00:45:37,102 --> 00:45:40,538
Ten times more →

608
00:45:40,605 --> 00:45:45,043
Hundreds of times, thousands of times →

609
00:45:45,110 --> 00:45:49,047
Momoko is important to me.

610
00:45:49,114 --> 00:46:00,125
♪～
